{"TopicId":219129,"ForumId":208,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal rotate/move in circle while moving straight forward at the pole of a CB","CreatedByName":"The0Frank","CreatedById":229719,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-31T13:42:41Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The0Frank","CreatedById":229719,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-31T13:42:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.4 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 5 3600 | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Nvidia RTX 2070 SUPER | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E16 GB DDR4 3200MHz\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen walking straight near the pole of Minmus one will be sucked into this \u0022singularity\u0022, wich happens to be exactly at the north pole.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen standing exactly at the north pole and pressing either \u0022W\u0022 or \u0022D\u0022/\u0022A\u0022 Jeb rotates very fast around himself and cant walk away from it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPressing \u0022S\u0022 or \u0022A\u0022/\u0022D\u0022 will free him. Whether you have to press \u0022A\u0022 or \u0022D\u0022 to get out depends on how you walked in i think (clockwise or counterclockwise).\u003Cbr\u003E\nYou can also fly away whith the jetpack.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cvideo class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 controls=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.global.core.embeddedvideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Csource type=\u0022video/mp4\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2024_01/KerbalSpaceProgram22023-08-3115-40-24-Trim.mp4.6451b288dacae21dd6599d73a0a2ed96.mp4\u0022\u003E\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/attachment.php?id=1270\u0026amp;key=8da3c8c5dbe574602c55ec92be8d8722\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221270\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022mp4\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKerbalSpaceProgram22023-08-3115-40-24-Trim.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/video\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-03T01:47:13Z\u0022 title=\u002201/03/2024 01:47  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 3\u0022\u003EJanuary 3\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anonymous Bug Reporter","CreatedById":231013,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-29T05:45:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Intel i7 8700 | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0rtx 3060 ti | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32 gb ddr4\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis happened to me when walking with a kerbal on moho a few km away from the mohole.\u00A0 When I pressed the w key, instead of walking forward, the kerbal would rapidly walk in circles.\u00A0 And when i say rapidly, i mean it looked like i was rotating my screen with a maxed out dpi on my mouse. Reloading an earlier save fixed this, but it was a very strange issue.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u00